  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth()+

library(dplyr)
##

gapminder %>% 
  filter(lifeExp>=70) %>% 
  group_by(continent) %>% 
  summarise(n=n()) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x=continent, y=n))+
  geom_col(aes(fill=continent))+
  labs(x = "",
       y="",
       title="3",
       subtitle=" 70   ()")
